{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now, what also happened was that some of the neighborhood kids were-- would stop playing with us because their parent told us not to, their parents.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some still would.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My parents, my father was always a defiant person, not prone to cooperate, so after a little while, we stopped wearing the stars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We just took our chances, so we wouldn't be subject to whatever would befall people who did wear the stars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we stopped wearing them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Parents as well, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which was against the rules and the law, but that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at one particular time, my father found someone [? who also ?] changed our name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that-- and we got some-- for-- for-- not fundamentally, but just for general public and also with some papers just in case we were checked on the street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, the-- as a matter of fact, in '42, in the-- in the spring of '42, they-- they required all people in the Jewish faith or ethnically Jewish should report, register, with the Judenrat, the Jewish councils, and they would then be issued special identity papers.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether they were Belgians or not, they would have a big-- they would be considered-- even if they were born elsewhere, even if they'd been there 20 years or 30 years-- they'd be called strangers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On their card would be a big stamp that would say 'Jew' in two languages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There would be a star of David.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There would also be the number of the-- of the registration number with the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was all, we didn't realize, all planning for, to be more efficient later on when they were starting to deport the people and arrest them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
